OL,3,CMulti-million-pound settlement reached
OL,4,Cin Celtic Boys Club historical abuse
OL,5,Ccase
OL,7,FA seven-figure payout has been agreed
OL,8,Ffor a lawsuit over claims of
OL,9,Fhistorical sexual abuse at Celtic Boys
OL,10,FClub, a law firm has said.
OL,12,FThompsons Solicitors, representing
OL,13,Faround 30 former players, said about
OL,14,F70 per cent of cases have been settled
OL,15,Fby Celtic Plc, with more settlements
OL,16,Fexpected in the coming weeks.
OL,18,FThe abuse was carried out by convicted
OL,19,Fpaedophiles James Torbett and Frank
OL,20,FCairney at the youth club, which was
OL,21,Fnot officially linked to Celtic FC.
