OL,9,Fus to fight for them on these
OL,10,Fdifficult cases and ensure their
OL,11,Fvoices were heard.
OL,13,F"This litigation has been made far
OL,14,Fmore complex and lengthy by the
OL,15,Fdefender, while our clients have acted
OL,16,Fwith resolute dignity throughout.
