OL,7,FA judge at Scotland's highest civil
OL,8,Fcourt, the Court of Session in
OL,9,FEdinburgh, previously allowed the
OL,10,Flegal action to proceed despite
OL,11,Fopposition from Celtic Plc's lawyers.
OL,13,FCeltic Plc's legal team argued the
OL,14,Fboys club was a separate entity, but
OL,15,FJudge Lord Arthurson ruled the case
OL,16,Fcould go ahead.
OL,18,FCeltic FC has been contacted for
OL,19,Fcomment but has previously said it is
OL,20,F"appalled by any form of historic
OL,21,Fabuse".
